quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,22,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: “Monsu mfrε wͻn a moadwen yε mo sε wͻ’ka Nyankopͻn ho no; wͻ’nni tumi a emu duro ketekete tesε aboboaa a ani ntumi nhu mpo wͻ soro anaa asaase so, na wͻ’nni ne mmienu mu kyεfa bi, na (Nyankopͻn) nni ͻboafoͻ bi a ͻfri wͻn mu"
  34,23,"Dwaatoa nso ho mma mfasoͻ wͻ Nehͻ, gyesε obi a (Nyankopͻn) bεma no kwan. Kosi sε ehuu befri wͻn (Soro abͻfoͻ no) akoma mu, (abͻfoͻ no) bεka sε: ”Asεm bεn na Mo Wura Nyankopͻn kaeε?” Wͻ’bebua sε: ”Nokorε’’. Ɔne Okokroko no, Ɔno ara nso ne Ɔkεseε no”"
  34,24,"(Nkͻmhyεni), kasε: “Hwan na ͻbͻ mo akͻnhoma firi soro ne asaase soͻ?” Kasε: “Nyankopͻn”. Ɛneε nokorε sε yεn, anaasε mo wͻ kwan tenenee paa so anaasε ͻyera pefee mu"
  34,25,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: Ye’mmisa mo fa yεn fͻdie ho asεm, na yemmisa yεn fa dwuma a modiiε no ho asεm"
  34,26,"Ka sε: “Ye Wura Nyankopͻn bεboa yεn nyinaa ano abom na afei Ɔde nokorε no abu yεn ntεm atεn. Ɔne Otemmufoͻ Nokwafoͻ no, na Ɔne Onimdefoͻ no“"
  34,27,"Ka sε: “Monkyerε me wͻn a mode wͻn ka (Nyankopͻn) ho sε ahokafoͻ no. Daabi, Ɔne Otumfoͻ no a Otumi ade nyinaa yε, Onyansafoͻ no"
  34,28,"(Nkͻmhyεni), Yε’somaa wo wͻ nnipa nyinaa hͻ sε anigyesεm ne kͻkͻbɔ ho bɔfoɔ, nanso nnipa pii nnim"
  34,29,"Deɛ wͻ’ka ne sε: “Ɛberε bεn na saa bͻhyε no bԑba, sε moyε nokwafoͻ ampa a?”"
  34,30,"Ka sε: “Ɛwͻ berε a yεde ahyε ama mo a montumi ntwe nnkͻ akyire anaasε animu dͻnhwere baako mpo “"